  <brief_title>Non-cancer Pain and Cognitive Impairment: A Disabling Relationship</brief_title>
  <official_title>Opioids Versus Extra Strength Acetaminophen for the Management of Moderate Persistent Non-cancer Pain</official_title>
  <sponsors>
